{title: We Three Kings}
{subtitle: Three Kings of Orient — John Henry Hopkins Jr., 1857 (publ. 1863)}
{key: Em}
{time: 3/4}
{tempo: 84}
{comment: Epiphany carol. Verses 2–4 are solos for each king; verses 1 and 5 are sung together.}

{start_of_verse: 1}
[Em]We three [B7]kings of [Em]Orient [B7]are
